songs.title: Fuck Yo Birthday
songs.lyrics:
[Prehook]
DJ it’s my birthday, my motherfucking birthday
Now won’t you play some shit to make the girls go wild
Yeah if you looking sexy and if you came to party
Then let me see you lose it when the beat drop right now
(Go! [x12]), fuck your birthday
(Go! [x12]), fuck your birthday

[Hook]
Tonight I’m gone be dancing, tonight I’m gone be drinking
Tonight I’m gone be flirting, cause fuck your birthday
I’m not asking permission, I only ask forgiveness
[?] live life so [?] fuck your birthday
Fuck your birthday [x4]

[Verse 1]
I don’t give a fuck, Imma play what I want
I don’t give a fuck, I’m tryna get drunk
I don’t give a fuck, Imma play what I want
And I don’t really care if you was born this month
Fuck your birthday, shake your ass
Fuck your birthday, take this glass
Fuck your birthday shake your ass
What them hoes screaming Class?

[Prehook 2]
DJ it’s my birthday, my motherfucking birthday
Don’t judge me if I get some random booty right now
Yeah if you looking sexy, and if you came to party
Then let me see you lose it when the beat drop right now
(Go! [x12]), fuck your birthday
(Go! [x12]), fuck your birthday

[Hook]

[Bridge][x2]
It’s my birthday, it’s it’s my birthday
Fuck your birthday, oh fuck your birthday

[Hook]

[Outro]
Fuck your birthday [x8]
